videos.headline: Howard says UK has the momentum required to win title
videos.description: Rhyne Howard says that after nine straight wins Kentucky is poised to give South Carolina all it can handle in the SEC Tournament Championship Game.

videos.headline: 3-point barrage pushes 7-seed UK past 3-seed UT
videos.description: With Rhyne Howard leading the way, Kentucky buries 12 of 24 three-pointers to take down Tennessee, 83-74, and advance to the SEC Tournament final.
